                        <interp inst="t18190526-64-person622" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  ; five pin-cloths, value 2 s.; two bed-gowns, value 2 s.; two skirts, value 1 s., and three aprons, value 18 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190526-64-victim624" type="victimName">
                     John 
